00:02:23.250 --> 00:02:28.110
breathing or have swelling of the lips, tongue
or throat.

00:02:28.110 --> 00:02:32.110
Rashes can come in many forms and, depending
on the cause, they can take days or even weeks

00:02:32.110 --> 00:02:33.110
to heal.

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:38.390
Rather than try to treat the rash on your
own, see a board-certified dermatologist.

00:02:38.390 --> 00:02:41.810
A dermatologist is trained to tell which rashes require more extensive medical testing and

00:02:41.810 --> 00:02:46.530
can properly diagnose the rash and determine
the best course for treatment.

00:02:46.530 --> 00:02:51.370
To find a dermatologist in your area, visit
